title: STATE assertion resolution
story: friendly-zoo
description: Pins the tester's entity resolution for [STATE] assertions —
  the reserved `player` keyword (works whatever the player entity is named)
  and alias resolution for the contains argument (transcript-tester P4).

---

> south
[OK: contains "Main Path"]

> east
[OK: contains "Petting Zoo"]

> take feed
[OK: contains "Taken"]
[STATE: true, player.inventory contains feed]
[STATE: true, player.inventory contains bag of animal feed]
[STATE: true, yourself.inventory contains feed]
[STATE: false, player.inventory contains camera]
